{"tid":288564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果射雕一開始係po係講故台，實比連登仔屌死","createTime":"2017-06-18T09:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T16:36:29.000Z","uid":75042,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40c40f51d9706019dae74187a58ea82ef3de332d","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:39:47.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇左⼀次射雕本書<br />\n入面啲巧合多到離哂譜<br />\n姐係我都明睇故咪駁故<br />\n但係啲巧合位真係過份左少少<br />\n如果投入咁睇既話，真係會睇到好撚燥<br />\n我都數唔到自己講左幾撚多次邊撚到有咁橋架<br />\n當有誤會既時候啲撚屌一定唔肯講清楚<br />\n我同黃蓉bb要長相廝守嗰陣一定有啲撚樣出黎阻撚柒住<br />\n如果而家po係連登一定比啲連登仔屌佢又冇甜又長又多巧合到on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申射雕係我第一本睇既金庸"},{"pid":"428e040989f104656c0b4dabf62533436741cdc5","tid":288564,"uid":4518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:40:47.000Z","msg":"咁你睇倚天屠龍記一定仲燥"},{"pid":"98123e217b87a0b4288744b85e584e8afd957423","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你睇倚天屠龍記一定仲燥</blockquote><br />\n不了，睇完呢本都已經慶過火屎<br />\n唔撚睇算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32738e1877fe20307e5bc9ce0cd0ff4f16bb452d","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5dfd9ce7e337abbc9bc107462045683f21ec960","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28317440fcc3e5cb637bb8e179437bbb14cd264","tid":288564,"uid":101706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f272edf26e8e5fe067373a103b08425889af8c5","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢老尾我幾廿萬次有機會同黃蓉bb長相廝守<br />\n佢就係咁搵啲撚屌出黎阻鳩住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd0d320a350533de54643fb66cfc49d18b598f3","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4ecb4f1c3813820673460515ee9c68f4603a34","tid":288564,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"正皮比樓主"},{"pid":"0afc6984579950dc55b0c938d640e13a2eb40a01","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正皮比樓主</blockquote><br />\n我.....我......我都不知如何感激你的恩情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d667302ca10ced5695a9c5cb24f93e9a32d606ca","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713d0e83614d18cee2ac2acccc23d087ca1d8a72","tid":288564,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:59:28.000Z","msg":"留名睇樓豬比狗咬"},{"pid":"47b370faa30298c8224f3d1ced7a34d6119b033a","tid":288564,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"講得啱，小說世界個地圖細撚過九龍，郁啲就撞到對家<br />\n<br />\n不過你都要諗下金庸作品係咩年代寫成<br />\n嗰陣讀者同作者諗嘢冇講求咁精密"},{"pid":"644efa35f1703791e1ef0ccd48d759dbe80dc78e","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講得啱，小說世界個地圖細撚過九龍，郁啲就撞到對家<br />\n<br />\n不過你都要諗下金庸作品係咩年代寫成<br />\n嗰陣讀者同作者諗嘢冇講求咁精密</blockquote><br />\n其實都唔係話唔精密既<br />\n只係佢太巧合得滯會令人睇嗰陣睇到燥<br />\n<br />\n頭盔先<br />\n唔係屌唔好睇只係覺得冇咁多巧合再好睇啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdbd917c70a6eac8781982a3bd5b180e4f87717","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇樓豬比狗咬</blockquote><br />\n護送me ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047689aa989c933a684aed22074bde5be31f8752","tid":288564,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"有冇例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3af2dbc5b91d666488f4b2f2508e2ddab62f3f1","tid":288564,"uid":1938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去到天南地北都可以撞返同一班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最屈機係茫茫大海都撞到，<br />\n周伯通仲要騎鯊魚出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6469f2584ccde9f0a6b91df564920d31f1328110","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去到天南地北都可以撞返同一班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最屈機係茫茫大海都撞到，<br />\n周伯通仲要騎鯊魚出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢到我睇到係咁屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗痴撚線咁都撞翻班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6147508cd749177324ce84f323db3bcfde4d83a1","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56222c302a0800eefd74282a4584717944c5a7de","tid":288564,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:56:27.000Z","msg":"最燥係密室療傷個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n齊曬人咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f426dbfa3c44c8234576240f044c367798190d57","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:09:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最燥係密室療傷個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n齊曬人咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真喎好似成個天下啲武林人士都去撚哂間屋仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b8eebd4eb22c08c3751ed0aff9e6ccedcbd5b8","tid":288564,"uid":55420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:13:30.000Z","msg":"我睇嗰陣都係咁諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過如果冇依啲巧合又好難睇到咁多角色之間嘅互動，到時又變咗冇咁好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32201cb16d69299d3dcefec850996c0f3b07c58","tid":288564,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:20:04.000Z","msg":"我細個睇嗰陣都係咁<br />\n<br />\n特別係密室療傷嗰到<br />\n<br />\n緊要關頭咁啱開唔到聲叫老豆<br />\n<br />\n咁啱又比人開到門<br />\n<br />\n一連串巧合"},{"pid":"6d36eacf169a06cc92a9fb3e35de27ad480bdde0","tid":288564,"uid":75042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇嗰陣都係咁諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過如果冇依啲巧合又好難睇到咁多角色之間嘅互動，到時又變咗冇咁好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巧合得滯就好似有啲on9🤔"},{"pid":"2e26d75fff727ebd4067c4c89b659278f